column2: select l.AGCNr as AGCNr, l.RAdeg_OC as ra, l.DECdeg_OC as dec, l.Vhelio as Vhelio, l.Dist as Dist, l.z as HI_z, N.objID as objID,    N.run, N.camcol, N.field, N.rerun, N.type, N.mode, N.cx, N.cy, N.cz, N.htmID, N.distance,    Nz.z as photo_Near_z from mydb.edge_lsbg_# as l   join Galaxy as G    join dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(l.RAdeg_OC,l.DECdeg_OC,#) as N ON G.objID = N.objID   JOIN photoZ AS Nz ON N.objID = Gpz.objID WHERE    Nz_z >= l.z-#*(#+l.z) and Nz_z <= l.z+#*(#+l.z) and    N.distance*#*l.Dist/# <= # ORDER BY distance
